# Project Overview

## 1. What This Platform Is

**Name:** Process Metrics Platform v2
**Type:** Open-source ETL + BI platform for calculating and visualizing software development team metrics
**Purpose:** Provide a free, customizable tool for automated collection, processing, and analysis of development metrics
**Deployment:** Runs locally on a personal computer or company server via a single Docker container, without any external cloud dependencies

---

## 2. Business Context

### Target Users
Project managers, delivery managers, agile coaches, team leads, and technical leads

### Problems Solved
- High cost of existing solutions with limited customization options
- Lack of a simple tool to connect multiple corporate systems as data sources
- Inability to define custom metrics or visualizations
- Cloud/SaaS usage is restricted or undesirable due to internal policies
- Complex BI integrations and expensive maintenance
- Most existing tools cannot properly import historical data

### Key Differentiators
- **Self-hosted:** Full control over data, structure, and visualization
- **Open-source:** Transparent, flexible, and license-free
- **Modular architecture:** Easily extendable with new connectors and metrics
- **No external dependencies:** Runs entirely locally or closely
- **Modern, maintainable stack:** Built on current ETL and BI technologies

---

## 3. Core Features

### Data Import and Processing
- Connect to Jira Cloud via REST API — [https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira]
- Load raw data using **dlt** — [https://github.com/dlt-hub/dlt-dbt-jira] & [https://dlthub.com/docs/dlt-ecosystem/verified-sources/jira]
- Transform data using **dbt** — [https://github.com/dbt-labs/dbt-core]
- Orchestrate tasks using **Prefect** — [https://github.com/PrefectHQ/prefect] & [https://docs.prefect.io/v3/get-started]
- Maintain full change history across data layers: `raw → clean → bi`

### Metrics Supported
- **Kanban:** Lead time, throughput, WIP
- **DORA:** Deployment frequency, lead time for changes, MTTR, change failure rate
- **Scrum:** Velocity, burndown, sprint predictability
- **Custom:** Extensible via the ETL service

### User Interaction
- **Metabase:** Self-service dashboards with customizable charts — [https://github.com/metabase/metabase] & [https://www.metabase.com/]
- **Admin panel:** Configure metric calculations, schedules, and access management
- **Grafana + Prometheus:** System monitoring and performance metrics — [https://github.com/grafana/grafana]&[https://grafana.com/], [https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus] &(https://prometheus.io/)
- **Prefect UI:** Visual management of data pipelines — [https://docs.prefect.io/ui]

